OL,5, A family has described suffering years 
OL,6, of racist abuse from neighbours that   
OL,7, led to their son asking if he could be 
OL,8, painted white.                         
OL,10,FThe couple and their two children were 
OL,11,Fforced to move from their home, schools
OL,12,Fand jobs, even fearing their house     
OL,13,Fwould be burned down.                  
OL,15,FTheir neighbours were fined but the    
OL,16,Fabuse continued, with racist graffiti  
OL,17,Fleft outside the family's home.        
OL,19,FThey have now been moved by Sovereign  
OL,20,FHousing, which has not commented.      
